One of Base’s core missions is to make Web3 accessible to everyone, not just crypto enthusiasts. By reducing transaction costs and improving user experience, Base lowers the barriers to entry for everyday users. Whether it’s trading NFTs, participating in DeFi protocols, or exploring decentralized social platforms, Base makes these activities affordable and intuitive.Moreover, Coinbase’s integration with Base allows users to seamlessly move funds between centralized and decentralized ecosystems. This fiat-to-crypto onramp is critical for onboarding non-crypto-native users, making Base a pivotal player in Web3’s mainstream adoption. Believing in Base is believing in a future where decentralized technology is as commonplace as the internet.

